<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="agree-with">agree with</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>同意；赞同：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>agree with one’s idea / opinion 
赞同某人的想法/意见</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I quite agree with him on the sports. 
我非常同意他在运动方面的观点。</p></div>

<p>注: agree with表示“同意”、“赞同”时，后常接人或表示“意见”、“看法”的词作宾语。  </p>
<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>与...相符；与...一致</strong></h4>
<p>to be the same as sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His words do not agree with his actions. 
他言行不一致。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>[常用于否定句] (食物等) 适合</strong></h4>
<p>(of food, etc.) be suitable for sb：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Too much meat doesn’t agree with her. 
她不宜吃太多肉。</p></div></div>